OL,3,CReform candidate stands down after
OL,4,Cappearing to do Nazi salute in photo
OL,6,FA Reform UK candidate for the upcoming
OL,7,FSenedd election has stood down citing
OL,8,Fhis mental health after photos of him
OL,9,Fappearing to strike a Nazi salute
OL,10,Fappeared online.
OL,12,FCorey Edwards will no longer be
OL,13,FReform's lead candidate for Pen-y-bont
OL,14,FBro Morgannwg constituency in the May
OL,15,F7 election for the Welsh Parliament.
OL,17,FA Reform UK Wales spokesperson said:
OL,18,F"Corey Edwards has informed us that he
OL,19,Fis stepping down as a candidate for
OL,20,Fthe Senedd election this May, citing
OL,21,Fissues with his mental health.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
