OL,3,CReform candidate stands down after
OL,4,Cappearing to do Nazi salute in photo
OL,6,F"We wish him well for the future and
OL,7,Fhope his privacy can be respected at
OL,8,Fthis difficult time."
OL,10,FIn a statement to ITV News, Corey
OL,11,FEdwards said the photo had been
OL,12,F"misinterpreted", while acknowledging
OL,13,Fhe had made "mistakes."
OL,15,F"There is a clear distinction between
OL,16,Fordinary use of the appalling gesture,
OL,17,Fcompared with me imitating a Welsh
OL,18,Ffootballer's use of it, or indeed
OL,19,FBasil Fawlty's walk," he said.
